ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This project (nanochat-turbo) is derived from the original "nanochat" project
by Andrej Karpathy (https://github.com/karpathy/nanochat).

nanochat-turbo adds the following enhancements:
- Mamba (Selective State Space Model) architecture support
- Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) and REFRAG capabilities
- Hybrid model configurations
- Extended documentation and testing infrastructure

If you use this software in your research, please cite the original nanochat:

@misc{nanochat,
  author = {Andrej Karpathy},
  title = {nanochat: The best ChatGPT that $100 can buy},
  year = {2025},
  publisher = {GitHub},
  url = {https://github.com/karpathy/nanochat}
}

All contributions maintain the MIT License and the spirit of the original
nanochat project: minimal, hackable, educational code for learning LLMs.

